nodes.text: FLO, also known as WA-7 or Wanda, was the nickname of a WA-7 waitress droid working at Dex's Diner on Coruscant. She once served Obi-Wan Kenobi when he came to the diner asking for help from Dexter Jettster.

FLO was voiced by Australian actress Susie Porter for Attack of the Clones, who also portrays Hermione Bagwa in the film. During shooting, Porter delivered her lines as both FLO and Bagwa, though in the final film FLO was chosen to have the speaking role.
